description.en: DICE is a TRC20 token on the TRON blockchain. WINk is a decentralized DApp platform. With a wealth of experience in game and platform development, the WINk team has been able to 'revolutionize' what Dapps can do for the wider community. According to the website FAQ, "win chance and payouts can be adjusted manually by the user" & "User's have full control of how much risk they are comfortable" with taking on. If the lucky number is within the criteria" users may be paid out according to the 'payout'. Losses will be deducted accordingly.
